    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_1997_Solutions_1997s_page_001_16",
    "text": "and so φ(g) commutes with φ(e) for all g. Next, we note that",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5568627450980392,
      0.4703030303030303,
      0.9192156862745098,
      0.4987878787878788
    ],
    "page": "exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_1997_Solutions_1997s_page_001",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_1997_Solutions_1997s_page_001_7",
    "text": "SO",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
