  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_1997_Solutions_1997s_page_001_17",
    "text": "and using the commutativity of φ (e), we deduce or (xy) = ψ(x) ψ(y), as desired.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.556078431372549,
      0.5381818181818182,
